node.text: How quickly they forget that I came from having nothing they forgot I shared a small bedroom with my 4 other brothers and sisters and my house of 7 all shared one bathroom! I went through whole school years with only 5 uniforms to recycle and every Christmas we all got gift cards to go out to dinner and see a movie so the reason I am how I am is to motivate little kids growing up the way I did! I give hope to all the kids that don’t want to be in the streets, that don’t see themselves graduating college, the kids that feel like they’re life isn’t as valuable as those in better positions! So yes you may see me as a bragger but I see me as an influencer trying to influence a positive and wealthy lifestyle!
